summary: Adds an argonian ranger class follower.
descriptionHtml:
I figured there aren't that many argonian followers on the nexus, so I made one. He is an argonian ranger called Wuleen-Ei.
You can find him At the Moorside Inn in Morthal. He is skilled with archery, one handed, light armor andÂ  somehow sneak.
He will not activate traps, and he levels automatically with the player and you can marry him.
Feel free to make requests.
I just started modding so I will only take follower requests and
mods that place/remove items,objects,NPCs etc in the gameworld outdoors or indoors anywhere.

The armor in the pictures: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3994/?
